  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This program will empower resource poor women of the community to become professional drivers and earn their livelihoods with dignity by taking up employment . Unemployed women are trained in driving for a period of three months and are placed as cab drivers or chauffeurs in corporate once the driving license is acquired.  Training curriculum includes communications skills, life skills and spoken English along with driving lessons. We empower them to become confident citizens in the community.</narrative>
  </description>
